n </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;Done&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">‚ùØ‚óØ Add the Google Analytics tracking script</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ‚óØ Add responsive images</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ‚óâ Add an automatic sitemap</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ‚óØ Generate a manifest file</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ‚óâ Add Markdown and MDX support</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ‚óØ Add Markdown </span><span class=\"mtk6\">support</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (without MDX)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>In here, I chhose javascript ( and I will mention how I turn js into ts in the future posts)<br>\nand style library, I shhose styled-components<br>\nwithout using CMS, I choose to use md file as blog-post</p>\n<p>After finish init, you can run this website right now<br>\nIn cmd, key in command<br>\n<code>npm run develop</code><br>\nthen you can run on the local server<br>\nOpen browser and go to: <a href=\"http://localhost:8000\">http://localhost:8000</a><br>\nYou will find it is there üéâ\nYou can see the change of website by editing this <strong>src/pages/index.js</strong> file<br>\nIn the future, I will share some of feature of what I did on this website</p>\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> js to ts</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> theme - darkmode</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> i18n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> deploy to github-page</li>\n</ul>\n<p>this 